Shark ya ji rauni a wani mai shekara 13 a California
A ranar Asabar, wani ɗan ƙaramin yaro ɗan shekara 13 ya ji rauni a hannun wani babban kifi mai suna shark sa'ad da yake hawan kifi a ranar farko na kakar kifi a California, in ji ma'aikata.
An kai harin ne da karfe 7 na safe a kusa da Beacon Beach a Encinitas.
Chad Hammel ya gaya wa KSWB-TV a San Diego cewa yana cikin ruwa tare da abokansa a safiyar Asabar da ya ji yaron yana kiran taimako sai ya zo tare da wasu mutane don su taimaka masa.
