Rashin hasashen da mahaukaciyar guguwar Rosa ta kawo, zai kawo ruwan sama mai yawa a kudu maso yammacin Amurka.
Kamar yadda aka annabta, Hurricane Rosa yana raguwa yayin da yake wucewa a kan ruwan sanyi na arewacin Mexico.
Amma, ruwan sama mai yawa zai zubo a arewacin Mexico da kuma kudu maso yammacin Amirka a kwanaki na gaba.
Rosa yana da isasshen iska na 85 mph (85 m.p.m.), Category 1 hurricane, daga 5 na safe ranar Lahadi, kuma an sanya shi mil 385 kudu maso yammacin Punta Eugenia, Mexico.
Ana sa ran Rosa za ta koma arewa a ranar Lahadi.
A halin yanzu, wani kwari da ke kan tekun Pacific yana fara yin siffa, yana tafiya zuwa gabas zuwa gabar yammacin Amurka. Yayin da Rosa Monday ke kusantar Baja California a matsayin guguwa mai zafi, za ta fara tura ɗumi mai zafi zuwa arewa zuwa kudu maso yammacin Amurka.
Rosa za ta kawo ruwan sama mai inci 10 a wasu sassan Mexico a ranar Litinin.
Bayan haka, a cikin kwanaki na gaba, za a yi ruwan sama mai yawa a kudu maso yamma, saboda yanayin zafi da ake gani a nan.
A cikin gida, ruwan sama mai inci 1 zuwa 4 zai iya jawo ambaliya mai haɗari, zubar da shara, da kuma yiwuwar ambaliyar ƙasa a cikin hamada.
