Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 sun kalli shari'ar Brett Kavanaugh
Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli cibiyoyin telebijin shida a ranar Alhamis domin kallon shaidar da babban mai neman a yanke masa hukuncin kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh da kuma Christiana Blasey Ford, matar da ta zarge shi da laifin aikata lalata a shekarun 1980s.
A halin yanzu, an ci gaba da samun rashin daidaito na siyasa, tare da masu watsa shirye-shirye suna katse shirye-shiryen yau da kullun don juyin Jumma'a: yarjejeniya da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya yi don FBI don gudanar da bincike na mako guda.
Ford ta gaya wa Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattijai cewa ta tabbata 100% cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade a cikin maye kuma ya yi ƙoƙarin cire tufafinta a wata bikin makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh, a cikin wata shaida mai ban sha'awa, ya ce ya tabbata da kashi 100 bisa 100 cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Wataƙila fiye da mutane miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli shi a ranar Juma'a, Nielsen ta ruwaito.
Kamfanin ya ƙidaya matsakaicin masu kallo a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samun adadi nan da nan ga sauran cibiyoyin sadarwa da ke nuna shi ba, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Nielsen wani lokaci yana da wuya a tantance yawan masu kallo a ofishi.
Don sanya shi cikin hangen nesa, wannan yana da yawan masu sauraro kamar na wasan ƙwallon ƙafa ko kuma na Academy Awards.
Fox News Channel, wanda masu sauraron sa suka goyi bayan Kavanaugh, ya kasance a gaban dukkan cibiyoyin sadarwa tare da masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a cikin sauraron sauraron ranar, in ji Nielsen.
ABC ta zo a matsayi na biyu da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS na da miliyan 3.1, NBC na da miliyan 2.94, MSNBC na da miliyan 2.89 kuma CNN na da miliyan 2.52, in ji Nielsen.
Bayan an gama shari'ar, mutane sun ci gaba da son jin labarin.
Flake ya kasance babban jigon wasan kwaikwayo na ranar Juma'a.
Bayan da 'yan jam'iyyar Republican masu ra'ayin mazan jiya suka fitar da sanarwar cewa za su kada kuri'ar su goyi bayan Kavanaugh, a safiyar ranar Juma'a aka samu Kavanaugh a CNN da CBS, inda masu adawa suka rika yi masa ihu yayin da yake kokarin hawa hawa wani babur zuwa wani kwamitin shari'a.
Ya tsaya na 'yan mintoci, idanunsa a rufe, yayin da CNN ke nuna hoton yadda ake zaginsa.
"Ina tsaye a gabanka", wata mata ta ce.
Kuna tsammanin yana gaya wa ƙasar gaskiya?
Aka ce masa, "Kai mai iko ne, amma waɗannan mata ba su da iko".
Flake ya ce ofishin sa ya fitar da sanarwa kuma ya tafi kofar dillalin, yana mai cewa zai kara da cewa a lokacin da kwamitin ke sauraro.
Kamfanonin sadarwa da na gida sun rufe kowa da kowa a cikin sa'o'i masu rai bayan haka yayin da Kwamitin Shari'a ya jefa ƙuri'a don inganta nadin Kavanaugh ga cikakken Majalisar Dattijai don kuri'a.
Amma Flake ya ce zai yi hakan ne kawai idan har FBI za ta duba tuhumar da ake yi wa dan takarar a mako mai zuwa, kamar yadda 'yan tsiraru na jam'iyyar Democrat suka bukaci.
Flake ya sami tabbaci ne ta hanyar tattaunawa da abokinsa, Sanata Chris Coons na Democrat.
Bayan ya tattauna da Coons da kuma wasu sanatoci, Flake ya yanke shawarar.
Flake ya yi amfani da ikon da ya nuna cewa 'yan Republican ba za su sami kuri'un da za su amince da Kavanaugh ba tare da wannan binciken ba.
Shugaba Trump ya ba da sanarwar binciken FBI game da zargin da aka yi wa Kavanaugh.
May ta zargi masu sukar da 'yan siyasa' kan Brexit
Firaminista Theresa May ta zargi masu sukar shirinta na barin Tarayyar Turai da yin " wasa da siyasar Birtaniya da kuma lalata al'amuran kasa " a wata hira da jaridar Sunday Times.
Firaministan Birtaniya Theresa May ta halarci taron jam'iyyar Conservative a Birmingham, Biritaniya a ranar 29 ga Satumbar, 2018.
A wata hirar da ta yi da jaridar, tsohon ministan harkokin wajen Birtaniya Boris Johnson ya ci gaba da kai wa gwamnatin Birtaniya hari kan shirin Chequers na ficewar Birtaniya daga Tarayyar Turai, inda ya ce duk wani shawara da aka bayar na Birtaniya da Tarayyar Turai su tara wa juna harajin da ake bi wa juna "batsa ne".
Wayde Sims: 'Yan sanda sun kama Dyteon Simpson da ake zargi da kashe dan wasan LSU
'Yan sanda sun kama wani da ake zargin da laifin kashe dan wasan kwallon kwando na LSU, Wayde Sims, mai shekara 20.
An kama Dyteon Simpson, mai shekara 20, an kuma tsare shi a kurkuku a kan zargin kisan kai na biyu, in ji 'yan sandan Baton Rouge.
Jami'ai sun fitar da faifan bidiyo na rikicin Sims da Simpson, kuma 'yan sanda sun ce Sims ya rasa tabarau a lokacin rikicin.
'Yan sanda sun gano ruwan tabarau a wurin, sun ce sun sami DNA na Simpson a kansu, in ji CBS affiliate WAFB.
Bayan sun yi wa Simpson tambayoyi, 'yan sanda suka ce ya yarda cewa ya kashe Wayde.
Lauyan ya ba da rahoton cewa an ba shi $350,000.
Ofishin binciken gawa na East Baton Rouge Parish a ranar Juma'a ya bayar da rahoton farko da ke cewa dalilin mutuwar shine rauni na bindiga a kai da wuyansa.
Ma'aikatar ta yaba wa rundunar 'yan sanda na Louisiana da suka tsere, da dakin binciken 'yan sanda na jihar, da' yan sanda na jami'ar Southern University da kuma mazauna yankin don taimakon da suka bayar a binciken da ya kai ga kama shi.
Daraktan Wasannin LSU Joe Alleva ya gode wa hukumar da ke kula da bin doka da ta dace saboda himmar da take yi wajen bin doka da kuma adalci.
Sims yana ɗan shekara ashirin.
The shida-faɗi-biyar-farin girma a Baton Rouge, inda mahaifinsa Wayne kuma buga wasan kwando ga LSU.
Ya yi 5.6 da 2.6 a wasan bara.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a, kocin kwando na LSU Will Wade ya ce kungiyar ta yi matukar damuwa da kuma firgita sakamakon mutuwar Wayde.
Wayde ya ce, "Wannan shi ne abin da ke damun ka a kowane lokaci".
Ruwan da ke fitowa daga dutsen da ke aman wuta a Mexico City
Ash da aka zubo daga dutsen Popocatepeti ya kai kudancin birnin Mexico.
Cibiyar Kula da Bala'o'i ta Kasa ta yi gargadin 'yan Mexico su guji zuwa wurin da za a yi ambaliyar a ranar Asabar bayan da ta yi rahoton cewa an samu tashin hankali a cikin dutsen mai fitad da iska, inda aka samu gas da toka guda 183 a cikin sa'o'i 24.
Cibiyar tana lura da girgizar ƙasa da yawa da kuma girgizar ƙasa.
Hotunan da aka wallafa a shafukan sada zumunta sun nuna yadda iskar gas ta rufe gilashin mota a unguwannin Mexico City kamar Xochimilco.
Masana kimiyyar ƙasa sun lura da karuwar aiki a dutsen mai fitad da wuta, wanda ke da nisan mil 45 (kilomita 72) kudu maso gabashin babban birnin, tun lokacin da girgizar ƙasa mai girman 7.1 ta girgiza tsakiyar Mexico a watan Satumbar 2017.
Wurin da ake ƙona wuta, da ake kira Don Goyo, ya soma aiki tun shekara ta 1994.
