Na farko, hanyar Hurricane Rosa ta kai ga ƙasa kusa da Baja California na Mexico.
Rosa, har ila yau, a ranar Lahadi da safe, yana da ƙarfin iska mai ƙarfin mil 85 a kowace awa, yana da nisan mil 385 a kudu da Punta Eugenia, Mexico, kuma yana motsawa zuwa arewa a mil 12 a kowace awa.
