Tun daga 2011, World Citizen ya ce ya yi rikodin sama da "ayyukan" miliyan 19 daga magoya bayansa, yana tallafawa da yawa daga manufofi daban-daban.
Ya ce, wadannan ayyukan sun taimaka wajen karfafa shugabannin duniya su sanar da kudade da manufofi da suka kai dala biliyan 37 wanda zai iya shafar rayuwar mutane sama da biliyan 2.25 nan da shekarar 2030.
A farkon 2018, kungiyar ta ba da rahoton alkawura da sanarwa 390 da suka haifar da ayyukanta, wanda aka riga aka biya ko aka tara aƙalla dala biliyan 10.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa, wannan kudaden da aka ba su, ya shafi kusan mutane miliyan 649 a duniya baki ɗaya.
Wasu daga cikin manyan alkawurran sun hada da Power of Nutrition, wata kawance ta masu saka jari da masu aiwatarwa da ke Birtaniya da suka kuduri aniyar "taimaka yara su kai ga cikakkiyar damar su", kuma suka yi alkawarin bayar da dala miliyan 35 ga Rwanda don taimakawa kawo karshen rashin abinci mai gina jiki a kasar bayan sun karbi fiye da 4,700 tweets daga 'yan Adam.
"Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatocin kasashe da kuma 'yan duniya kamar ku, za mu iya sanya rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki a matsayin wani ɓangare na tarihin", in ji Jakadan Power of Nutrition Tracey Ullman a lokacin wani taron jama'a a London a watan Afrilu na 2018.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce bayan ayyuka sama da 5,000 da aka yi don neman Birtaniya ta inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga iyaye mata da yara, gwamnatin ta sanar da bayar da tallafi ga wani shiri, mai suna, Power of Nutrition, wanda zai kai ga mata da yara miliyan 5 da ke fama da matsalar abinci mai gina jiki.
