Moscow ta sha nanata cewa aikin da aka yi na dala biliyan 11 na bututun Nord Stream 2, wanda zai ninka karfin bututun da ake da shi zuwa mita miliyan dubu dari, aikin tattalin arziki ne.
Kremlin ya yi jayayya cewa tsananin adawar da Washington ke yi wa aikin ya samo asali ne daga dalilan tattalin arziki kuma ya nuna rashin adalci.
"Na yi imani cewa mun yarda cewa makamashi ba zai iya zama hanyar matsawa ba kuma masu amfani da shi ya kamata su iya zaɓar masu samar da su", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha, Aleksandr Novak, bayan ganawa da Sakataren Makamashi na Amirka, Rick Perry, a Moscow a watan Satumba.
Ra'ayin Amurka ya haifar da adawa daga Jamus, wanda ya sake tabbatar da sadaukar da kai ga aikin.
Babban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus, wato Federation of German Industries (BDI) ta yi kira ga Amurka da ta guji shiga cikin manufofin makamashi na Tarayyar Turai da kuma yarjejeniyar da aka kulla tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
"Ina da babbar matsala idan wata ƙasa ta uku ta tsoma baki a cikin arzikinmu na makamashi", in ji Dieter Kempf, shugaban Tarayyar Masana'u ta Jamus (BDI), bayan ganawarsa da Angela Merkel, shugabar gwamnatin Jamus, da kuma Vladimir Putin, shugaban ƙasar Rasha.
Sanata daga Massachusetts ya ce Elizabeth Warren za ta "yi tunani sosai" don tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa a 2020
A ranar Asabar, sanata Elizabeth Warren ta Massachusetts ta ce za ta "yi la'akari sosai" da tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben tsakiyar lokaci.
A wani taron gari a Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ta tabbatar da cewa za ta yi la'akari da tsayawa.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, kuma hakan ya hada da mace a kan mataki mafi girma", in ji ta a cewar The Hill.
"Bayan 6 ga Nuwamba, zan yi tunani sosai game da tsayawa takarar shugaban ƙasa".
Warren ta yi ba'a game da Shugaba Donald Trump a lokacin taron garin, yana cewa yana "kai kasar zuwa hanyar da ba daidai ba.
"Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokradiyarmu", in ji ta.
Warren ta kasance mai faɗar albarkacin baki a wajen sukar Trump da kuma nadin da ya yi na Brett Kavanaugh a matsayin babban mai shari'a.
A wani sakon Twitter da ya wallafa a ranar Juma'a, Warren ya ce "hakika muna bukatar binciken FBI kafin mu yi zabe".
