Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da "tsokana" da "tallace-tallacen farfaganda"
Mako guda bayan da wata jaridar kasar Sin ta buga wani shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka da ke yaba wa cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da Sin, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da yin amfani da 'yan jarida na Amurka wajen yada farfagandar.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi tsokaci game da shigar da China Daily a cikin littafin Des Moines Register, jaridar da ta fi yawan sayarwa a jihar Iowa, a ranar Laraba bayan da ya zargi China da yin katsalandan a zaben da aka yi a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da China ta musanta.
Zargin da Trump ya yi wa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka ya nuna abin da jami'an Amurka suka fada wa Reuters, wani sabon mataki ne a wani yunkurin da Washington ke yi na kara matsawa China lamba.
Duk da yake al'ada ce ga gwamnatocin kasashen waje su yi talla don inganta kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington a halin yanzu suna cikin wani rikici na cinikayya da ya kai ga daidaita farashin kayayyaki da ake shigowa da su.
Farashin da China ta yi a baya a yakin cinikayya an yi niyyar a doke masu fitar da kayayyaki ne a jihohi kamar Iowa da suka goyi bayan Jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, in ji masana na China da Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa na tsawon lokaci, wanda babban mai fitar da kayayyakin noma ne zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
China, in ji Branstad a cikin wani talifin da ke cikin Des Moines Register na Lahadi, "yanzu ta ƙara tsananta zalunci ta wajen buga tallace - tallacen farfaganda a jaridarmu ta 'yanci.
"Ta hanyar yaɗa farfagandarsu, gwamnatin China ta yi amfani da al'adun Amurka na 'yancin faɗar albarkacin baki da kuma 'yancin 'yan jarida ta hanyar saka talla a cikin Des Moines Register, in ji Branstad.
"A bambance, a kan titin da ke kan titin a nan Beijing, za ka ga ƙarancin muryoyi masu banbanci, ba za ka ga ainihin yadda jama'ar Sin ke nuna bambancin ra'ayi game da yanayin tattalin arzikin Sin ba, saboda kafofin watsa labarai na ƙarƙashin ikon kwaminis na Jam'iyyar Kwaminis ta Sin", in ji shi.
Ya daɗa cewa "ɗaya daga cikin manyan jaridu na ƙasar Sin ta ƙi buga labarinsa", ko da yake bai faɗi ko wane jarida ba.
