"Ba batun kuri'ar kwamitin ba ne ko kuma kuri'ar karshe ko kuma Kavanaugh ya zama alkali, batun shi ne yadda 'yan Republican suka bi da ita da kuma yadda suka bi da ita", in ji Guy Cecil, darektan Priorities USA, wata kungiya da ke taimakawa wajen zaben 'yan Democrat, ga gidan talabijin.
Amma Amurkawa sun ɗan rarrabu kan wanda za su gaskata bayan shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh, tare da wasu da ke goyon bayan na biyun.
Wani sabon binciken da aka yi na YouGov ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin dari na masu amsa sun yarda da shaidar Ford, yayin da kashi 35 suka ce sun yarda da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce suna tunanin Kavanaugh ya yi da'awar cewa ya yi da'awar cewa ya yi da'awar ko kuma ya yi da'awar cewa ya yi da'awar a lokacin da yake ba da shaida, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari kawai suka ce Ford ya yi da'awar.
Bayan da Flake ya yi kira, FBI na binciken tuhumar da Ford ya yi, da kuma aƙalla wata mai gunaguni, Deborah Ramirez, in ji The Guardian.
A makon da ya gabata, Ford ta shaida wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa a karkashin rantsuwa cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade a lokacin da yake da shekaru 17 a lokacin da yake cikin maye.
Ramirez ya yi ikirarin cewa babban mai shari'a ya fallasa mata al'aurarsa yayin da suke halartar wani biki a lokacin da suke karatun Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo a duniya yana shirin kafa sabuwar yanar gizo don ya fafata da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya kafa wani kamfani da ke kokarin yin gasa da Facebook, Amazon da kuma Google.
Sabon aikin da masanin fasaha ya yi, Inrupt, kamfani ne da ya gina kan dandalin buɗe tushen Berners-Lee, Solid.
Solid ya ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda aka adana bayanan su da kuma waɗanne mutane aka ba damar samun damar zuwa waɗanne bayanai.
A cikin wata hira ta musamman da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi ba'a cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce " mamaye duniya. "
Ya ce game da aikin: "Dole ne mu yi hakan yanzu.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasaha na Solid don ba da damar mutane su ƙirƙiri nasu "aikin ajiyar bayanan kan layi na sirri" ko POD.
Yana iya ƙunshe da jerin sunayen abokan hulɗa, jerin abubuwan da za a yi, kalanda, laburaren kiɗa, da sauran kayan aikin sirri da na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna nan a lokaci guda a cikin wani mai bincike.
Abu na musamman game da adana bayanan sirri ta yanar gizo shi ne cewa yana da gaba ɗaya a hannun mai amfani wanda zai iya samun damar yin amfani da irin wannan bayanin.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan "haɓaka mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar kamfanin HUB John Bruce, shine kamfanin ya kawo albarkatu, tsari da ƙwarewar da ta dace don taimakawa samar da Solid ga kowa.
Kamfanin a halin yanzu ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro wanda IBM ta saya, masu haɓaka a kan ma'aikatan da aka ƙulla don yin aiki a kan aikin, da kuma al'umma na masu ba da agaji.
Farawa daga wannan makon, masu haɓaka fasaha daga ko'ina cikin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta hanyar amfani da kayan aikin da aka samo a shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa tattaunawa da "Facebook da Google game da ko za su gabatar da wani babban sauyi, inda za a sauya tsarin kasuwancin su gaba ɗaya.
"Ba ma tambayar su".
A cikin wani rubutu da aka buga a Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa Inrupt "na'urar da aka kafa don samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu don taimakawa wajen kare mutunci da ingancin sabon gidan yanar gizo da aka gina akan Solid. "
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya sauya intanet lokacin da ya kafa gidan yanar gizo na duniya a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin da suka gabata, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Duk da cewa ya kaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da zama wanda ya kafa kuma darektan kungiyar yanar gizo ta duniya, Gidauniyar Yanar gizo da kuma Cibiyar Bayanai.
"Ina da kwarin gwiwa sosai game da wannan zamani na yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
