Lt.kol Honorabul Bernard Vann ya sami lambar yabo a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, a cikin harin Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Amma, bayan kwanaki huɗu, wani mai harbi ya kashe shi, bai san cewa ya sami daraja mafi girma a rundunar sojojin Britaniya ba.
