Desert Island Discs: Tom Daley ya ji 'ƙananan' game da jima'i
Dan wasan tseren ruwa na Olympics Tom Daley ya ce ya girma da "rashin mutunci game da jima'i" amma hakan ya ba shi kwarin gwiwar zama mai nasara.
Ɗan shekara 24 ya ce bai sani ba sai ya shiga makarantar sakandare cewa "ba kowa ba ne yake so ya yi abin da nake so".
Da yake magana a farkon shirin Radio 4 Desert Island Discs wanda Lauren Laverne ya gabatar, ya ce ya bayyana ra'ayinsa game da 'yancin gay don ya ba wasu "bege".
Ya kuma ce zama iyaye ya sa bai damu da cin nasara a Wasannin Olympic ba.
Mai gabatar da shirin na tsawon shekaru Kirsty Young, ta yi watanni tana rashin lafiya.
Daley ya bayyana a matsayin wanda aka yi watsi da shi a shirin Laverne na farko, ya ce ya ji "ƙananan" fiye da kowa ya girma daban, saboda "ba a yarda da zamantakewa don son yara maza da mata ba".
Ya ce: "Har wa yau, waɗannan jiye-jiyen na ƙanƙantawa da kuma na dabam, su ne ainihin abubuwan da suka ba ni ƙarfi da kuma kuzari na yin nasara".
Ya ce yana son ya nuna cewa shi "wani abu ne" don kada ya ɓata wa kowa rai sa'ad da aka gano cewa shi ɗan luwaɗi ne.
Dan wasan da ya lashe kofin zinare sau biyu a gasar Olympics ya zama fitaccen dan adawa na LGBT, kuma ya yi amfani da bayyanar da ya yi a gasar Commonwealth ta bana a Australia don yin kira ga kasashe da yawa da su haramta luwadi.
Ya ce ya yi dariya domin yana farin ciki cewa zai iya rayuwa a fili ba tare da wani sakamako ba kuma yana son ya ba wasu "bege".
Gwarzon zakaran gasar duniya sau uku ya ce faduwa cikin soyayya da wani mutum da ya hadu da shi a shekarar 2013 "ya kama shi da kallo".
Daley ya auri Oscar mai shekaru 20 da haihuwa a bara, amma ya ce banbancin shekarun ba shi da matsala.
"Idan ka fuskanci abubuwa da yawa a irin wannan lokacin"  ya tafi wasannin Olympic na farko lokacin yana ɗan shekara 14 kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu daga ciwon daji bayan shekara uku  ya ce yana da wuya a sami wani a shekarunsa da ya fuskanci irin wannan yanayi na farin ciki da baƙin ciki.
Ma'auratan sun haifi ɗa da ake kira Robert Ray Black-Daley a watan Yuni, kuma Daley ya ce "dukkan ra'ayinta" ya canza.
"Idan ka tambaye ni a shekarar da ta shige, za ka ce, 'Ina son na ci zinare,' " in ji shi.
"Amma ka sani, akwai abubuwa da suka fi zinare na Olympics girma.
Gwarzon zinari na na Olympics shi ne Robbie".
An haifi ɗansa mai suna Robert wanda ya mutu a 2011 yana da shekaru 40 bayan an gano shi da cutar kansa ta kwakwalwa.
Daley ya ce mahaifinsa bai yarda cewa zai mutu ba, kuma daya daga cikin abubuwan karshe da ya tambaye shi shi ne ko sun sami tikiti zuwa London 2012  saboda yana son ya kasance a layin farko.
"Ban iya gaya masa 'ba za ka kasance a nan don zama a cikin front row, Dad,'" ya ce.
"Na riƙe hannunsa sa'ad da ya daina numfashi, kuma bayan da ya daina numfashi kuma ya mutu ne na gane cewa ba a iya cin nasara a kansa ba", in ji shi.
A shekara mai zuwa, Daley ya yi takara a gasar Olympics ta 2012, inda ya lashe tagulla.
"Na san cewa wannan shi ne abin da na yi mafarkinsa a rayuwata, wato yin tsalle a gaban 'yan wasan ƙasarmu a gasar Olympics, wannan shi ne abin da ya fi kyau", in ji shi.
