Mickelson ya yi rashin nasara kuma ya janye daga Ryder Cup na ranar Asabar
Ba'amurke Phil Mickelson zai kafa tarihi a ranar Lahadi lokacin da ya buga wasa na 47 na Ryder Cup, amma zai bukaci ya sake samun kyakkyawan tsari don kaucewa zama abin takaici.
Mickelson, wanda ke wasa a karonsa na 12 a cikin wasan shekara-shekara, ya yi ritaya daga wasan ta kyaftin Jim Furyk don wasannin kwallaye hudu da hudu na ranar Asabar.
Maimakon zama a tsakiyar wasan, kamar yadda ya kasance sau da yawa a United, mai nasara sau biyar a Majors zai raba ranarsa tsakanin zama jagora, yana aiki a kan wasan motsa jiki, yana fatan gyara abin da ya ɓace.
Ko da a lokacin da ya fi kowa tsada, ba shi ne ya fi kowa yin tsalle ba, saboda haka, dan shekara 48 ba shi ne mutumin da ya fi dacewa da tsalle-tsalle a filin Le Golf National ba, inda dogon filin da aka yi a baya ya zama abin da ya fi dacewa da duk wanda ya yi ta yawo.
Kuma kamar dai ba shi da ƙalubalen da ya isa, Mickelson a ranar Lahadi ya yi tsere a wasansa na tara da Francesco Molinari, wanda ya yi nasara a gasar Open ta Burtaniya, wanda ya yi nasara a wasanni huɗu a wannan makon tare da sabon mai zuwa Tommy Fleetwood.
Idan 'yan wasan Amurka, da ke da maki hudu a baya, suka fara wasannin 12 na wasan kwaikwayo, wasan Mickelson zai iya zama abin da ya dace.
Furyk ya furta amincewarsa ga mijinta, ba cewa yana da wani abu da zai ce ba.
Furyk ya ce: "Ya fahimci aikin da yake yi a yau, ya yi mini taɓawa a baya, ya rungume ni, ya ce zai yi kyau gobe.
"Ya yi yawa amincewa da kansa.
Yana cikin Gidan Jarumawa kuma ya ba da gudummawa sosai ga waɗannan rukunin a baya da kuma wannan makon.
Wataƙila ban taɓa tunanin cewa zai buga wasanni biyu ba.
Na yi tunanin da yawa, amma wannan ita ce hanyar da abubuwa suka kasance kuma wannan shi ne abin da muka yi tunanin ya kamata mu yi.
Yana son ya kasance a wurin, kamar kowa".
Mickelson zai wuce Nick Faldo a ranar Lahadi don zama dan wasan da ya fi taka leda a gasar Ryder.
Wannan na iya nuna ƙarshen Ryder Cup wanda bai taɓa daidaita da ainihin abubuwan da ya cim ma ba.
Mickelson yana da nasara 18, 20 ya ci nasara da rabi bakwai, kodayake Furyk ya ce kasancewarsa ya ba da gudummawar abubuwa masu yawa ga ƙungiyar.
"Yana da ban dariya, yana da baƙar magana, yana da basira, yana son ya yi dariya, kuma yana da kyau a kasance da shi a cikin rukunin", in ji shi.
"Ina ganin 'yan wasan matasa sun ji daɗin yin wasa da shi, wanda abin farin ciki ne.
Yana ba da fiye da wasa kawai".
