Babban taron Donald Trump mai hadari tare da mataimakin babban lauya Rod Rosenstein na iya "a jinkirta shi da wani mako" yayin da ake ci gaba da gwagwarmaya kan babban alkalin kotun kasar Brett Kavanaugh, Fadar White House ta ce a ranar Lahadi.
Rosenstein yana lura da aikin mai ba da shawara na musamman na shari'a Robert Mueller, wanda ke binciken tsoma bakin Rasha a zaben, alaƙa tsakanin masu goyon bayan Trump da Rasha da kuma yiwuwar saɓani da doka ta shugaban.
Ko Trump zai kori mataimakin babban lauyan, kuma ya yi barazana ga 'yancin Mueller, ya kasance abin da Washington ta yi ta baƙar magana a cikin watanni.
A farkon wannan watan, New York Times ta ba da rahoton cewa Rosenstein ya tattauna yiwuwar ɗaukar na'urar rikodin don yin rikodin tattaunawa tare da Trump, da kuma yiwuwar cire shugaban ta hanyar 25th Amincewa.
