Trump ya ce zai "fi son" Rosenstein ya yi murabus, amma sai aka dage taron don kauce wa rikici da kotun majalisar dattijai inda Kavanaugh da ɗaya daga cikin matan da suka tuhume shi da laifin lalata, Dakta Christine Blasey Ford, suka ba da shaida.
