Girgizar ƙasa da Tsunami a Indonesiya
A kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da tsunami da ya afkawa birnin Palu da ke Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, in ji jami'ai, kuma ana sa ran adadin zai ƙaru.
Tare da sadarwa da aka kashe, ba da agaji jami'an ba zai iya samun wani bayani daga Donggala Regency, wani yanki arewa na Palu cewa shi ne mafi kusa da tsakiyar 7.5 girgizar kasa.
A Palu, an kai mutane fiye da 16,000 zuwa inda za su tsira bayan bala'in ya auku.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birni ne na lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, wanda ke kan iyakar ƙananan bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da ƙididdigar yawan jama'a na 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekara 40 da kafuwa lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku.
Donggala ita ce wata ƙasa mai ruwan sama da ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 mi) a gabar tekun arewa maso yamma na tsibirin Sulawesi.
Yankin, yanki ne na gudanarwa a ƙarƙashin lardin, yana da kimanin yawan jama'a na 299 200 a cikin 2017.
Kamun kifi da noma sune ginshiƙan tattalin arzikin lardin Central Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Har ila yau, hakar ma'adinai na nickel yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma ya fi mayar da hankali a cikin Morowali, a gefen gabar tsibirin Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunamis sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka wuce, in ji Hukumar Kawar da Bala'o ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya hallaka ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami kuma ya buge Donggala ta yamma a 1996 kuma ya yi sanadiyyar mutuwar mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake kira Pacific Ring of Fire, kuma tana yawan fuskantar girgizar ƙasa.
Ga wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da aka yi a shekarun baya:
2004: Wani babban girgizar ƙasa a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesiya a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ya haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi ƙasashe 14, ya haifar da mutuwar mutane 226,000 a gabar Tekun Indiya, tare da fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Aukuwar girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afka wa gabar Sumatra a ƙarshen watan Maris da kuma farkon watan Afrilu.
An kashe ɗarurruwa a tsibirin Nias, a bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girman 6.8 ya shafi kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, wanda ya haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi kudancin gabar teku kuma ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: An yi girgizar kasa mai girman 7.6 kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Fiye da mutane 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai girman 7.5 ta afkawa daya daga cikin tsibiran Mentawai, kusa da Sumatra, wanda ya haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa ya afkawa masarautar Pidie Jaya a Aceh, wanda ya haifar da halaka da fargaba lokacin da aka tunatar da mutane game da lalacewar girgizar kasa da tsunami a shekarar 2004.
A wannan karon ba tsunami ba ne, amma gine-gine da suka rushe da kuma girgizar ruwa sun kashe mutane fiye da 100.
2018: Manyan girgizar kasa sun afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, inda mutane sama da 500 suka mutu, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Wannan girgizar ta halaka dubban gine-gine kuma ta jefa dubban masu yawon buɗe ido cikin haɗari na ɗan lokaci.
An kama ɗan fari na Sarah Palin a kan zargin cin zarafin iyali
An kama Track Palin, ɗan fari na tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma mataimakin shugaban ƙasa Sarah Palin, bisa zargin cin zarafin iyali.
Palin, mai shekara 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, an kama shi ne a kan zargin cin zarafin mata a gida, da yin katsalandan a kan rahoton cin zarafin mata a gida, da kuma yin tsayayya da kama shi, in ji wani rahoto da 'yan sandan jihar Alaska suka fitar a ranar Asabar.
A cewar rahoton 'yan sanda, ya ƙwace wayar wata matar da ya sani sa'ad da ta kira 'yan sanda don ta kai rahoto game da laifin da ake zarginsa da shi.
An tsare Palin a Mat-Su Pre-Trial Facility kuma ana tsare da shi a kan $500 na rashin tabbacin, KTUU ta ruwaito.
Ya bayyana a kotu a ranar Asabar, inda ya ce "ba shi da laifi, tabbas" lokacin da aka tambaye shi abin da yake so, in ji cibiyar sadarwar.
Palin yana fuskantar laifuka uku na aji A, wanda ke nufin zai iya ɗaure har shekara guda da kuma biyan tarar dala 250,000.
Ana kuma tuhumarsa da wani laifi na aji B, wanda ke da hukuncin kwana daya a gidan yari da kuma biyan tarar $2,000.
Wannan ba shi ne karo na farko da aka kai wa Palin tuhumar aikata laifi ba.
A watan Disamba na 2017, an tuhume shi da yin lalata da mahaifinsa, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda ta ba da rahoton zargin da ake yi mata.
A yanzu haka, ana sauraron shari'ar a Kotun Tsofaffin Sojoji na Alaska.
A cikin watan Janairun 2016, an tuhume shi da aikata laifukan cin zarafin gida, da shiga tsakani a cikin rahoton aikata laifukan cin zarafin gida, da kuma mallakar bindiga yayin da yake cikin maye, dangane da lamarin.
Sai budurwarsa ta ce ya yi mata duka a fuska.
Sarah Palin ya sami suka daga kungiyoyin tsoffin sojoji a cikin 2016 bayan da ta danganta halayyar ɗanta ga PTSD sakamakon aikinsa a Iraqi.
