Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya suna neman hukuncin kisa da ba a saba gani ba ga wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci na NYC
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da laifin ta'addanci a birnin New York da ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a taba yi wa wani babban laifi a jihar ba tun a shekara ta 1953.
Saipov, mai shekara 30, an ce ya yi amfani da wata motar haya ta Home Depot wajen kai hari a kan hanyar keke a kan titin West Side a Lower Manhattan don kashe masu tafiya da kafa da kuma wani mai hawan keke da ke kan hanyarsa a watan Oktoba.
Don a ba da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su nuna cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas "da gangan" kuma ya yi musu "mummunan rauni", in ji sanarwar da aka ba da na neman a yanke masa hukuncin kisa da aka shigar a Kudancin Gundumar New York.
Dukkan waɗannan zarge-zargen suna da hukuncin kisa, kamar yadda takardar da kotu ta rubuta ta nuna.
Makonni bayan harin, babban kotun tarayya ta tuhumi Saipov da laifuka 22, wanda ya haɗa da laifuka takwas na kisan kai don cin hanci, wanda masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da shi a cikin shari'ar aikata laifuka, da kuma zargin tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Wannan yaƙin ya bukaci "tsara da kuma shiri sosai", in ji masu gabatar da kara, kuma suka kwatanta yadda Saipov ya yi shi da "munanan halaye, da mugunta, da kuma lalata".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da rauni, lalacewa da asara ga dangi da abokai na Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco, "in ji sanarwar da aka yi niyya.
Biyar daga cikin waɗanda aka kashe 'yan yawon buɗe ido ne daga ƙasar Argentina.
Shekaru goma sun shige tun da Kotun Kudancin New York ta yi shari'ar ɗaukan kisa.
An yanke wa wanda ake zargi, Khalid Barnes, hukuncin kisa na masu sayar da kwayoyi biyu, amma a karshe aka yanke masa hukuncin rai da rai a watan Satumban 2009.
A cikin shari'ar da aka yanke a New York, hukuncin kisa na karshe da aka yi a kan wani mutum shi ne na Julius da Ethel Rosenberg a shekara ta 1953. An kashe su ne bayan da aka yanke musu hukuncin kisa a kan laifin da aka yi musu na yin leken asiri a lokacin da ake yaƙin basasa a Soviet Union shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
Dukansu Rosenberger aka kashe ta hanyar lantarki a kan Yuni 19, 1953.
Saipov, ɗan asalin Uzbekistan, bai nuna nadama ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun kotu.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya gaya wa masu bincike cewa yana jin daɗin abin da ya yi.
Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa an yi masa wahayi ne bayan ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayar sa, kamar yadda ake tuhumar.
Ya kuma nemi a nuna masa tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya ce ba shi da laifi a kan tuhume-tuhume 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce "hakika an yi musu ba'a" da hukuncin da aka yanke.
"Muna tunanin cewa yanke hukuncin kisa maimakon a ba da rai na rai ba tare da yiwuwar saki ba zai iya tsawanta ciwon da ya faru ga duk wanda abin ya shafa", in ji Patton.
A baya, masu kare Saipov sun nemi masu tuhumar su daina neman a yanke musu hukuncin kisa.
