Dundee Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants Ƙungiyar Elite League
Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallo biyu a wasan da Giants suka buga da Dundee
Dundee Stars sun yi nadama kan rashin nasarar da suka yi a wasan Elite League da suka yi da Belfast Giants a ranar Juma'a ta hanyar lashe wasan da suka yi da Dundee 5-3 a ranar Asabar.
Giants sun sami nasarar cin kwallaye biyu na farko ta hanyar jefa Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun buga wasan gida kafin Dwyer ya sake dawo da Giants.
Francois Bouchard ya kawo Dundee daidai kafin biyu Lukas Lundvald Nielsen-a raga ya kafa nasara.
Wannan shine nasara ta uku a cikin Elite League a wannan kakar wasa ta Adam Keefe wanda ya fara da rasa wasanni, sannan ya ci Dundee 2-1 a Belfast a daren Juma'a.
Wannan shi ne karo na hudu na wannan kakar tsakanin bangarorin, tare da Giants sun lashe wasanni uku da suka gabata.
Dwyer ya bude kwallo a minti na hudu a 3:35 daga Kendall McFaull taimako, tare da David Rutherford yana taimakawa lokacin da Beauvillier ya ninka jagorancin minti hudu daga baya.
A cikin abin da ya kasance lokacin buɗewa mai aiki, Sullivan ya dawo da ƙungiyar gida cikin wasa a 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya zama mai kula da daidaitawar Cownie a 15:16.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da Giants sun yi nasara har zuwa lokacin da ya ci ta biyu a wasan a karshen rabin lokaci.
The home team regrouped da kuma Bouchard sake samu su a cikin wani wasa da wani iko burin a 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun hada kai don taimakawa Nielsen ya ba Dundee damar jagorantar wasan a karon farko a ƙarshen rabin na biyu kuma ya tabbatar da nasara tare da ƙungiyarsa ta biyar a tsakiyar rabin karshe.
Giants, waɗanda suka yi rashin nasara a wasanni huɗu cikin biyar da suka gabata, za su yi wasa a gida a Milton Keynes a ranar Jumma'a.
Mai kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama ya mutu don tabbatar da daruruwan jirgin sama zasu iya tserewa girgizar kasa
Wani mai kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama a Indonesiya ya zama jarumi bayan ya mutu sa'ad da ya sa jirgin da ke ɗauke da ɗaruruwan mutane ya tashi lafiya.
Sama da mutane 800 sun mutu, wasu kuma sun bace bayan da wata babbar girgizar kasa ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi a ranar Juma'a, inda ta haifar da tsunami.
Har yanzu akwai girgizar kasa mai karfi a yankin kuma mutane da yawa sun makale a cikin kwararar ruwa a cikin garin Palu.
Amma, duk da abokan aikinsa da suka gudu domin rayukansu, Anthonius Gunawan Agung ɗan shekara 21 ya ƙi ya bar matsayinsa a hasumiyar da ke kula da filin jirgin sama na Mutiara SIS Al-Jufri a Palu.
Ya tsaya ba ya motsi don ya tabbata cewa jirgin Batik Air mai lamba 6321 da ke kan titin jirgin a lokacin ya tashi lafiya.
Sai ya yi tsalle daga hasumiyar da ke kula da zirga - zirgar ababen hawa sa'ad da ta faɗo.
Daga baya ya mutu a asibiti.
Mai magana da yawun Air Navigation Indonesia, Yohannes Sirait, ya ce wannan matakin da aka ɗauka ya ceci rayuka da yawa, in ji rahoton ABC News na Australia.
Mun shirya wani jirgin sama daga Balikpapan, Kalimantan, don ya kai shi babban asibiti da ke wani birni.
Abin baƙin ciki, mun yi hasararsa da safiyar yau kafin jirgin ya isa Palu.
"Mun yi baƙin ciki sosai da wannan labarin", in ji shi.
A halin yanzu, hukumomi suna fargabar cewa adadin mutanen da suka mutu zai iya kai dubbai, kuma hukumar bayar da rahoton bala'i ta ƙasar ta ce an hana mutane shiga ƙauyukan Donggala, Sigi, da Boutong.
"An yi imanin cewa adadin wadanda suka mutu na karuwa ne saboda gawarwakin da dama na cikin gine-gine, yayin da wasu da dama kuma ba a kai ga gano su ba", in ji mai magana da yawun hukumar Sutopo Purwo Nugroho.
Raƙuman ruwa da suka kai tsawon kafa 20 (mita 6) sun ragargaza Palu, wanda za a yi jana'izar mutane a ranar Lahadi.
Jiragen sama na soja da na kasuwanci suna shigo da kayan agaji da kuma kayayyaki.
Risa Kusuma, wata uwa 'yar shekara 35 ta gaya wa Sky News: "Abulance yana kawo gawawwaki a kowane minti.
Ruwa mai tsabta yana da wuyar samu.
Ana cutan ƙananan ƙasashe a ko'ina".
Jan Gelfand, shugaban kungiyar Red Cross ta duniya a Indonesia, ya gaya wa CNN: "Kungiyar Red Cross ta Indonesia tana neman masu tsira, amma ba mu san abin da za su samu ba.
Wannan bala'i ne, amma zai iya zama da muni sosai.
Shugaban kasar Indonesia Joko Widodo ya isa Palu a ranar Lahadi, inda ya gaya wa sojojin kasar cewa, "Ina rokon ku duka da ku yi aiki dare da rana don kammala duk wani aikin da ya shafi aikin kwashe mutane.
Shin kuna shirye? " CNN ta ruwaito.
A farkon wannan shekarar, girgizar ƙasa ta auku a Lombok, inda mutane fiye da 550 suka mutu.
Hadarin jirgin Micronesia: Air Niugini ya ce yanzu mutum daya ya bace bayan hadarin jirgin
Kamfanin jirgin sama da ya yi jigilar wani jirgin da ya yi hatsari a wani tafkin Tekun Fasifik a Micronesia, ya ce an rasa wani mutum guda, bayan da ya ce fasinjoji 47 da ma'aikatan jirgin sun tsira daga jirgin da ya nitse.
Kamfanin Air Niugini ya bayyana a cikin wata sanarwa cewa tun da yammacin Asabar ba su sami labarin wani fasinja namiji ba.
Kamfanin jirgin ya ce yana aiki tare da hukumomin yankin, asibitoci da kuma jami'an bincike don neman mutumin.
Kamfanin jirgin bai amsa ba nan da nan ga buƙatun ƙarin bayani game da fasinja, kamar shekarunsa ko kuma ƙasashensa.
Jirgin ruwan da ke yankin ya taimaka wajen ceto sauran fasinjoji da ma'aikatan jirgin bayan da jirgin ya yi ruwa a lokacin da yake kokarin sauka a filin jirgin saman Chuuk Island.
A ranar Juma'a, jami'ai sun ce an kai mutane bakwai asibiti.
Kamfanin jirgin ya ce fasinjoji shida sun kasance a asibiti a ranar Asabar, kuma dukkansu suna cikin yanayi mai kyau.
Ba a san ainihin dalilin da ya sa jirgin ya rushe ba kuma ba a san ainihin yadda abin ya faru ba.
Kamfanin jirgin sama da kuma rundunar sojan ruwa ta Amirka sun ce jirgin ya yi sauka a bakin tekun kusa da hanyar jirgin.
Wasu da suka ga wannan abin sun yi zaton cewa jirgin ya yi tsalle ne.
Wani Ba'amurke da ke cikin jirgin, Bill Jaynes, ya ce jirgin ya yi sauka a ƙasa sosai.
"Wannan abu ne mai kyau", in ji Jaynes.
Jaynes ya ce shi da wasu sun yi tafiya cikin ruwa mai zurfi har suka kai bakin ƙofar gaggawa na jirgin da ya nitse.
Ya ce, ma'aikatan jirgin sun tsorata kuma sun yi kururuwar tsoro, kuma ya ji rauni a kai.
Rundunar sojan ruwa ta Amurka ta ce, jiragen ruwa da suke aiki kusa da gyaran wani mashigi, sun yi amfani da jirgin ruwa mai tururi don su kai mutane zuwa bakin tekun kafin jirgin ya nutse a cikin ruwa mai zurfin kafa 30.
Bayanai daga cibiyar kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama sun nuna cewa mutane 111 sun mutu a cikin shekaru 20 da suka gabata a cikin hadarurrukan jiragen sama da ke rajistar PNG, amma Air Niugini ya shiga cikin daya.
