A ranar Asabar ne jihar ta rufe shari'ar ta a lokacin da ake sauraron sauraren karar da aka shigar kan wani mutum da ake zargi da cinna wa wata mata 'yar Mississippi wuta a shekarar 2014.
Manazarcin sashen shari'a na Amurka Paul Rowlett ya yi awoyi a matsayin gwani mai bincike a fannin binciken leken asiri.
Ya bayyana wa masu sauraron yadda ya yi amfani da bayanan da aka yi a wayar salula don ya san yadda mutumin da aka kama, Quinton Tellis, ɗan shekara 29, da kuma wanda aka kashe, Jessica Chambers, 'yar shekara 19, suka yi a daren da aka kashe ta.
Rowlett ya ce ya sami bayanan wuri daga wayoyin hannu da yawa wanda ya nuna cewa Tellis yana tare da Chambers a daren mutuwarta, wanda ya saba da da'awarsa ta baya, The Clarion Ledger ta ruwaito.
Bayan bayanan sun nuna cewa wayarsa ta hannu tana gidan Chambers a lokacin da ya ce yana tare da abokinsa Michael Sanford, sai 'yan sanda suka je suka yi magana da Sanford.
Sanford ya shaida a ranar Asabar cewa ba ya cikin gari a wannan ranar.
Lokacin da masu gabatar da kara suka tambaye shi ko Tellis yana da gaskiya lokacin da ya ce yana cikin motar Sanford a wannan daren, Sanford ya ce yana "kwanciya, saboda motar ta tana cikin Nashville".
Amma abin da ya sa ba a yi wannan maganar daidai ba shi ne, Tellis ya ce ya san Chambers na kusan makonni biyu sa'ad da ta rasu.
Bayanan waya sun nuna cewa sun yi sati ɗaya ne kawai suna tare.
Rowlett ya ce bayan mutuwar Chambers, Tellis ya share saƙonnin Chambers, kira, da kuma bayanan tuntuɓar daga wayar sa.
