"Zan fada muku wannan, idan ba zai gaya wa Majalisa gaskiya ba ko kuma FBI, to bai cancanci ya kasance a Kotun Koli ba, amma ya cancanci ya kasance a kotun da yake yanzu", Pelosi ta ce.
