Tashin wutar yaƙin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da Sin ya kasance mai saurin ji, kuma yayin da yaƙin ya yi nisa da ƙarewa, rashin jituwa tsakanin ƙasashen na iya zama mai amfani ga Beijing a cikin dogon lokaci, in ji masana.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya fara yin gargadi a farkon wannan shekarar ta hanyar sanya haraji kan manyan kayayyakin da kasar Sin ke fitarwa, da suka hada da bangarorin hasken rana, karfe da kuma aluminum.
