Ministan harkokin wajen Syria ya ce, kasar na "shirye" don dawo da 'yan gudun hijira
Syria ta ce a shirye take ta karɓi 'yan gudun hijira da za su koma gida, kuma ta yi kira ga jama'a da su taimaka wajen sake gina kasar da ta yi shekaru fiye da bakwai ana yaki.
Ministan Harkokin Waje Walid al-Moualem ya yi jawabi a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, yana cewa yanayi a ƙasar yana samun sauƙi.
Yau, yanayin ƙasa ya fi kwanciyar hankali da tsaro saboda ci gaba da yaƙi da ta'addanci, ya ce.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da gyara wuraren da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata.
Yanzu, an sami dukkan yanayi na 'yan gudun hijirar da za su koma ƙasarsu bisa son rai, bayan da ta'addanci da kuma matakan tattalin arziki da suka shafi rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum suka yi musu barazana.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa sama da 'yan Siriya miliyan 5.5 sun tsere daga kasar tun lokacin da yakin ya barke a shekarar 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da suke da zama a ƙasar suna bukatar taimako.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Siriya za ta yi maraba da taimako don sake gina kasar da ta rushe.
Amma ya nanata cewa ba za ta karɓi taimako ko taimako na wasu ƙasashe da suka tallafa wa mamayar ba.
Turai ta yi nasara a gasar Ryder a birnin Paris
Team Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder ta 2018 kuma ta doke Team Amurka da ƙimar 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National a waje da Paris, Faransa.
A yanzu dai, Amurka ta yi rashin nasara a Turai sau shida a jere, kuma ba ta yi nasara a gasar Ryder ba a Turai tun shekara ta 1993.
Turai ta sake samun kambinta sa'ad da rukunin da kyaftin Thomas Bjorn na Denmark ya ja da baya ya sami maki 14.5 da ake bukata don a ci Amirka.
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya sha wahala a mafi yawan gasar, ya ba da T-Haw a cikin ruwa a rami na 16 na par-3 kuma ya ba da wasa ga Francesco Molinari.
Dan wasan Italiya Molinari ya yi ta yin fice a dukkan zagaye kuma ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasa 1 daga cikin 4 da suka taba zuwa 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth ya yi 5&4 a hannun dan wasan da ya fi kowa daraja a Turai, Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark.
Dan wasan da ya fi kowa daraja a duniya, Dustin Johnson, ya ci Ingila da ci 2 da 1 a kan Poulter wanda ya yi wasa a gasar Ryder Cup ta ƙarshe.
Tsohon sojan gasar cin kofin Ryder sau takwas, dan kasar Spain Sergio Garcia, ya zama gwarzon gasar zakarun Turai a duk lokacin da ya zira kwallaye 25.5 a wasan da ya yi.
"Ba na yawan yin kuka, amma a yau, na kasa yin hakan.
Shekarar nan ba ta kasance da sauƙi ba.
Ina godiya ga Thomas da ya zaɓe ni kuma ya gaskata da ni.
Ina farin ciki, ina farin ciki da samun wannan kofin.
Wannan game da kungiyar ne kuma ina farin ciki da na taimaka", in ji Garcia cikin nutsuwa bayan nasarar Turai
Ya ba da fitila ga ɗan ƙasarsa John Ram wanda ya ci Tiger Woods 2 & 1 a wasan guda a ranar Lahadi.
Rahm mai shekara 23 ya ce: "Ina alfahari sosai da na doke Tiger Woods, na girma ina kallon mutumin nan.
Woods ya rasa dukkan wasanninsa hudu a Faransa kuma yanzu yana da rikodin 13-21-3 a gasar Ryder Cup.
Wannan baƙon lamari ne daga ɗaya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasa a kowanne lokaci kuma ya lashe manyan lakabi 14 na biyu ga Jack Nicklaus.
Team USA sun yi ta gwagwarmaya a duk karshen mako don neman filin da ya dace da ban da Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau waɗanda suka buga wasan golf mai ƙarfi a duk faɗin gasar.
Bayan wani mummunan rauni da aka yi, Kyaftin din Amurka Jim Furyk ya yi magana a madadin tawagarsa: "Ina alfahari da wadannan mutane.
Akwai ya kasance lokaci wannan safiya a lokacin da muka sanya wasu kadan zafi a kan Turai.
Mun shafe shi.
Ku yi wa Thomas ladabi.
Shi kyaftin ne mai ban mamaki.
Dukan 'yan wasa 12 sun yi wasa mai kyau.
Zan yi aiki tare da PGA na Amurka da kuma kwamitin Ryder Cup, kuma za mu ci gaba.
Ina ƙaunar waɗannan 'yan'uwa maza 12 kuma ina alfahari da na zama shugabansu.
Dole ne ka riƙe kafarka a kan ƙwanƙwasa.
Mun fi su.
